{
  "info": {
    "name": "Atomadic API",
    "description": "Formally verified AI safety APIs for autonomous agents.\n\nEvery safety guarantee is mathematically proved in Lean 4 — not benchmarked, not tested, proved.\n\n**Authentication**\n- Free endpoints: no authentication required\n- Paid endpoints: set the `API_KEY` variable, or use x402 micropayment flow (see docs)\n\n**Variables**\n- `API_BASE`: base URL (default: https://atomadic.tech)\n- `API_KEY`: your API key (get one at /pay)\n\n**x402 Flow (keyless)**\n1. Call any paid endpoint without credentials\n2. Receive HTTP 402 with payment details\n3. Send USDC on Base L2, Polygon, or Solana\n4. Retry with `X-Payment-Proof` header",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "API_BASE",
      "value": "https://atomadic.tech",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "API_KEY",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
